sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant E as express.json
    participant H as Handler POST
    participant R as Resposta
    C->>E: POST /tarefas<br>Content-Type: application/json<br>{"titulo": "Estudar"}
    Note over E: Parseia JSON do body<br>disponibiliza em req.body
    E->>H: req.body = { titulo: "Estudar" }
    H->>H: Valida, cria tarefa
    H->>R: res.status(201).json(nova)
    R->>C: 201 Created<br>{"id": 1, "titulo": "Estudar"}
